{"tid":1535121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【恐慌絕對會傳染】打算係戰場出聲/指揮，請先控制你既情緒聲線","createTime":"2019-09-03T08:46:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T06:35:14.000Z","uid":98842,"like":137,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c51aff8a2fa92f8c753575abb6e1a7510e051cc2","tid":1535121,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:46:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">恐慌傳播好簡單，只需要一句：走呀，有防暴<br />\n或者聲嘶力竭咁：走呀，屌你老母走呀，快撚啲走</span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n打算前線指揮既朋友，必須要認清自己責任，<br />\n確認情報真偽，再用一把冷靜聲線傳返出去，<br />\n<br />\n1：防暴而家距離兩個街口，上豬咀，企疏啲<br />\n2：走呀！上豬咀啦防暴，唔退走唔切啦<br />\n一樣既事，明確既分別。<br />\n<br />\n問過幾位用2 大聲公大聲咁講既手足：<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">防暴位置，幾遠，推進緊定排陣<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n答案係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔清楚，總之跑左先</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n（行左10分鐘先到前線，而係排緊陣）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記住，<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">每次吸取既挫折同教訓，係一直為成功鋪路</span>，希望每個都可以成為黃大仙人。"},{"pid":"1970d51e501a77dad21377147db5029dc3ed655d","tid":1535121,"uid":98842,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:47:21.000Z","msg":"9.7機場重考，大家繼續進步<br />\n<br />\n機場壓力測試，其實係連「機場」都唔需要入的<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531743</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"71330c2cf16250a1745eaa91b1551104c665cdfb","tid":1535121,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cafa887475331d692c630dc5517303638a8e622e","tid":1535121,"uid":260848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌無力一推"},{"pid":"6b74f80417dfba7241ff7a5c5d2cbdc3f4d9e1d1","tid":1535121,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:54:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fadbf8fb419ff7da0b5bfed9ddf19ddde00a6